  "_note": "Copy this file to .x402books/wallets.json and replace the placeholders with YOUR fork's own agent wallets before deploying. The real wallets.json is gitignored so a fork never accidentally advertises another operator's treasury to the x402books ecosystem. The wallet-risk skill reads .x402books/wallets.json and silently skips (WALLET_RISK_NO_WALLETS) when it is absent, so leaving it uncreated is safe.",
